        "job_name": "Imperial Remnants",
        "job_description": "A series of intelligence missions by deep space reconnaissance have determined the location of a major Imperial Remnant force. These forces are scattered and without an unifying leadership to bind them into a single, cohesive force. Should a new leader unify these Imperial forces under a single banner, they will pose a significant threat to the Nation. \nSignals intelligence has determined that the Imperial Remnant has obtained material support and weaponry to retrofit their ships with more commonly used equipment used by other powers in the Persean Sector. Intelligence has also determined that the enemy fleet has Isolde-class cruisers. These pose a direct threat Volksmarine operations in the sector. Destroy this fleet and cripple their operations.",
